6:
Wallet? Check! Shopping list from
Alk? Check! Ready to go with all my
gear!
31: I believe we've arrived at the East.
36:
Yeah, now that you mention it... this
IS Yamato! How did we get here?
41: A transfer error, if I had to guess.
46:
Oh, no, no, no! Don't tell me my bad
luck landed us here!
49:
It was probably an error on my part.
I'm sorry, Suzuka.
54:
Y-you don't have to apologize! It
was an accident, right? Then it's
nobody's fault!
56:
We should figure out how we're
gonna get back!
59:
Once we locate the World Flipper,
we can return to Starview Village.
64:
Sounds like a plan—I'll keep you safe
in the meantime!
67:
Well, well... look what the wind
dragged in. We thought you'd gone
for good, Suzukaze. And the girl with
you...
69:
We require her for further
observation. Let's go.
73:
We are close, but if we go any
further, Yamato—
83:
Have you heard the latest rumors in
the city? Apparently there is a
celestial maiden among us.
89:
Those rumors are doubly interesting,
now that I see the presence of the
diviner with you.
97:
Don't tell me... you've grown to care
for her?
99:
If you know what's good for you, you
WILL comply!
112:
Enough delusions. You have been
and always will be a ninja... A tool to
be used.
130: That's a big fat no from me!
135:
There's no WAY I'm double-crossing
one of my first real friends!
151: I'll protect you, no matter what!
157:
You fool! Do you understand what
you're doing?!
159:
I think it's pretty obvious, don't you
think?
164: Everyone! How did you get here?
173:
Look alive, Ninja Girl! The faster we
take care of these punks, the sooner
we can grab some after-quest
drinks!
183:
*pant* *pant* Sorry, but... I'm
quitting the ninja life.
186:
Stella has nothing to do with the
disappearances. I know you won't
believe me, and the evidence looks
bad, but I'm telling the truth.
188:
Hunt me down all you want. Just
leave my friends out of it.
195: That was pretty formal for you.
200:
I can pull it off when the occasion
calls for it!
208:
Don't need to tell me twice! Starview
Village, here we come!
